{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "本章题为\"飞狐归天\"。叶开在古城追踪一对伪装成卖鸡老夫妇的江湖人物。他在驴车下发现躲藏者，识破其异常——在万人瞩目的混乱中竟不回头观看。叶开揭露老太婆和老头子是制造混乱掩护进城的阴谋者。老头子和老太婆突然分头逃窜，叶开追上老头子，认出他是\"飞狐\"杨天——一个伪装成老头子的魔教\"布达拉天王\"。杨天身受重伤，因在热水中泡澡暴露了伤势。叶开追问其入魔教的原因，杨天发笑后倒地身亡，死因是中毒而非外伤。杨天死后，伪装成老太婆的王寡妇现身，对杨天之死毫无悲伤。她挑逗叶开引用\"朋友妻不可戏\"的江湖俗语，叶开冷淡应对并以打伤韩贞鼻子之事警告她离开。叶开返回城中，发现宋老板和巨人同样死于针孔般的小伤口。最后，一名伪装成捕快的叶开旧友以逮捕为名，实则邀请叶开赴宴。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来认不出你的，只可惜你来的时候太巧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们进城的时候，正是最乱的时候，我本来也不会看见你们，可惜那时我恰巧站在竹竿上。那时进城来的人，也不止你们两个，本来我就算看见你们，也绝不会疑心，可惜你们的样子却跟别的人都不一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我们的样子有哪点跟别人不一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自己不知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一点也不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我觉得我们的样子连一点特别的地方都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也就因为你们的样子连一点特别的地方都没有，所以才特别。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那时候别人的样子都很特别……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们连看都不看一眼，只因为你们早就知道那地方会发生那件事，只因为那件事根本就是你们安排的，好掩护你们进城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我看错了你，我想不到你竟是这么样一个人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是怎么样个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是个该死的人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是你受了伤，我本来追不上你的。你的轻功，果然是天下无双的轻功。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你已认出了我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫忘记我们本来是朋友，老朋友。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我没有你这种朋友。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的伤很重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然受了重伤，就不该泡在热水里的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是江湖中的人，无论谁都难免受伤的，这并不是见不得人的事，你为什么要瞒我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_tian",
      "speaker_name": "杨天",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要瞒着我，只因为你算准我一定已知道孤峰受了伤，你要瞒着我，只因为你就是魔教中的'布达拉天王'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的聪明我也一直都很佩服，所以我实在想不通，像你这么样一个人，为什么要入魔教？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是你的男人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他活着时是的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自己的男人死了，无论什么样的女人都会有点难受的。但我却看不出你有一点难受的样子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我本就是寡妇。他并不是我第一个男人，我看见过的死人，也不止他一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "无论什么事，只要习惯了，也就不会难受了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是你杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你应该知道他早已受了伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是他刚才还是活生生的一个人，为什么现在忽然死了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他受的伤并不重，中的毒却很重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他虽然用药物勉强压制住毒性，可是一奔跑用力，毒势就发作了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道他是什么人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道'飞狐'杨天不但轻功高，而且还有很多别的本事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "治伤疗毒，也是他的专长之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但是你现在却还要说他是被毒死的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上只要有一种他不能解的毒，他就可能被毒死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "真的不是你杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我从不杀朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他真是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要他做过我一天朋友，就永远是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也听说过你是他的朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我还听说过一句话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "朋友妻，不可戏，要戏朋友妻，要等朋友死后戏。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这句话我好像也听你说过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在他已死了，我还活着，你……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你见过韩贞没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那小子本来也在打我的主意，可惜我一看见他就想吐。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为他的鼻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他那鼻子看起来简直就像是烂茄子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道他那鼻子怎么会变成那样子的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是不是被人打的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道是被谁打的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不但知道，而且知道得比谁都清楚。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一定就是被你打的，对不对？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你现在最好赶快走，带着你的男人走，好好的替他埋葬。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "王寡妇",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你要我走？为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为现在我的手很痒，你若再不走，我保证你的鼻子很快就要变得跟韩贞一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_kuai",
      "speaker_name": "捕快",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你走不了的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_kuai",
      "speaker_name": "捕快",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你伤了两条人命，居然还敢露面，你的胆子倒不小。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_kuai",
      "speaker_name": "捕快",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "人命关天，王法如炉，你就算有天大的胆子，我也不怕你不招。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟想把我怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_kuai",
      "speaker_name": "捕快",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不管怎么样，先关起来再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_kuai",
      "speaker_name": "捕快",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "然后再用上好的人参炖一只鸡，做四五样精致的下酒菜，烫几壶陈年的竹叶青，请你连酒带菜一起吃下去。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我算明白了，原来你想胀死我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    }
